{"tid":2257343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"步履蹣跚搖晃 習健康惹關注  中醫︰或腰部勞損","createTime":"2020-10-25T05:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T07:13:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0811345889ebd5b83e1bd360f86907157c1b8aa","tid":2257343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/XWBNFI5P2ZDFXCELQ4D4C74RRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FXWBNFI5P2ZDFXCELQ4D4C74RRM%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=562ce974\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FXWBNFI5P2ZDFXCELQ4D4C74RRM%2F&h=6acee73f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/XWBNFI5P2ZDFXCELQ4D4C74RRM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n步履蹣跚搖晃 習健康惹關注 <br />\n中醫︰或腰部勞損<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【再現疲態】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：朱鎔基醫院過92歲生日 精神不錯<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】年屆67歲的國家主席習近平，其健康狀況再受關注。他前天在北京人民大會堂發表紀念抗美援朝70周年講話，以強硬措詞警告要「迎頭痛擊」侵犯和分裂國家的任何人或勢力，但在離場時卻被發現步履蹣跚，身體向兩側搖晃。有中醫師表示，單憑影片觀察走路姿勢，難以判斷習的身體出現甚麼問題，但不排除習可能出現腰部勞損或腰腿痛，導致要用椅子借力才能起立及坐下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/92kyvP_b1kt9kmOrFYr0uzthG30=/720x429/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MJZFIUFSCZGAVKUMMLKZSZA7V4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F92kyvP_b1kt9kmOrFYr0uzthG30%3D%2F720x429%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMJZFIUFSCZGAVKUMMLKZSZA7V4.jpg&h=f32e7912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習近平前天在人民大會堂發表抗美援朝紀念講話後，步離會場時被指步姿有異。<br />\n<br />\n習近平前天借紀念抗美援。。。。。。。。。。。。。，習在紀念大會結束後步出會場時，明顯跟進場時的步行姿態有明顯分別，步履蹣跚，身體向兩側搖晃，頭部亦稍微向前傾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qcGwkyaqtvg75sVgGNgdFTRohiQ=/1277x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G5S2YTU4QREYPB43FNSQTL2KEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqcGwkyaqtvg75sVgGNgdFTRohiQ%3D%2F1277x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG5S2YTU4QREYPB43FNSQTL2KEQ.jpg&h=c6b749c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入場生猛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JtPpzC7h6RXMaqq4jtYibJhUAC0=/1144x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7J5ITPIMCRBSTEU5U4AYMETHQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJtPpzC7h6RXMaqq4jtYibJhUAC0%3D%2F1144x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7J5ITPIMCRBSTEU5U4AYMETHQU.jpg&h=8187bc06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n離場蹣跚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o1r4N_4tPhyylL3fTC37lmZ7ZSk=/1147x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DJRCMADLQJDTXEYVNMH3P4TYGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo1r4N_4tPhyylL3fTC37lmZ7ZSk%3D%2F1147x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDJRCMADLQJDTXEYVNMH3P4TYGQ.jpg&h=29c3fab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n頻頻睇稿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民︰包子不注意飲食<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台並剪輯了外媒拍攝的習近平進場和離場片段以作比對。片段所見，習在進場時昂首闊步，但離場時步伐明顯較慢，在離開座椅後的首幾步更顯得腳步浮浮。有網民跟帖說：「讀四十分鐘能保證沒有錯別字可不容易，精神高度集中，累壞了。」、「沒別的，就是講話太累了，說那麽多太費神，畢竟一大把年紀了，平時操勞國事又沒時間鍛煉身體。」、「長那麽胖，脂肪肝，高血壓，高血糖。習包子也不知道注意一下飲食？」<br />\n<br />\n這並不是習近平的健康狀況首度惹來外界揣測。去年3月25日，習近平國事訪問法國，。。。。。。。。。。。。其間至少六度咳嗽和喝水，至講話尾聲咳至兩度停頓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1dJuT40gytY-axY3QvT1dhKoCjs=/1287x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6KDHNTSS35C23PTFBWKTI2DLVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1dJuT40gytY-axY3QvT1dhKoCjs%3D%2F1287x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6KDHNTSS35C23PTFBWKTI2DLVA.jpg&h=e71e383a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習去年3月訪問法國要借力坐下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒︰或肌肉關節問題<br />\n<br />\n中醫師徐澤昌向本報稱，片段所見習近平走路時一跛一跛，站起來時有點吃力，有可能是腰部勞損或腰腿痛問題所致，但單憑影片難以判斷。本身是泌尿外科醫生的立法會醫學界議員郭家麒表示，單憑觀察一個人的腳步，難以判斷其健康問題。「人如果很疲倦都會走得較慢，習近平六十多歲，如果平日休息不足、壓力大或者是心理壓力，都會出現疲倦的表現。另外，這亦有可能是肌肉或關節問題，例如退化性關節炎或髖關節退化，亦會造成步行蹣跚，腳步不是太順暢。」<br />\n<br />\n據新華社報道，習近平近兩個星期的工作日程表安排得頗頻密。。。。。。。。。。。。。這次習被拍得出現疲態，未知是否與近日出席多場公開活動有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YRfdy-chzFBMFt6A3fr0j3IMNBE=/1790x599/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SYM75KP7DBHCJOIZYAZGKXKOBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYRfdy-chzFBMFt6A3fr0j3IMNBE%3D%2F1790x599%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSYM75KP7DBHCJOIZYAZGKXKOBQ.jpg&h=0fbee293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"604d0ccf57728efcc24c43a0bd0de9e50648aee2","tid":2257343,"uid":183758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">快撚啲死</span>"},{"pid":"7d816f90916b171df3e7cd3bb58e155d839f7e6a","tid":2257343,"uid":32675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:36:26.000Z","msg":"係咪同奶媽扑得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f69b17dfc1f3c5779b5b89fe90b9721e48ed29","tid":2257343,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"屌,食到肚漲啫"},{"pid":"066b801f3f77f7e4d6bed3fefc197ae48a565c0f","tid":2257343,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d816f90916b171df3e7cd3bb58e155d839f7e6a","tid":2257343,"uid":32675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:36:26.000Z","m